 />\n旅遊區啲人講蝗語都無問題"},{"pid":"bedaea34a8ad1ae7f7ffe0dcc7442baf2e88c829","tid":178644,"uid":100331,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-30T03:01:54.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>無問題 夜晚唔好去酒吧區 住宿住明洞/弘大 獨遊韓國係無問題 （去左4次韓 有1次自己去）</blockquote><br />\n你自己一個去住邊？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n明洞/弘大 <br />\n住酒店"},{"pid":"cb16ce4f0fdbf70938272b6ee2dd73aa52c23f06","tid":178644,"uid":52561,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-30T03:31:19.000Z","msg":"仲有唔好搭的士 好多都係會兜路or呃錢<br />\n盡量搭地鐵啦"},{"pid":"51dc195d078ecca518b8a683b9ddd56921c1d207","tid":178644,"uid":100331,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-30T04:58:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>仲有唔好搭的士 好多都係會兜路or呃錢<br />\n盡量搭地鐵啦</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n的士 黑色最貴 其他顏色都可以搭<br />\n最好有韓文地址 或者叫佢也係地鐵站幾號出口落<br />\n因為啲司機好撚蠢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"824492581e9bd6165e73d527898b2b6aec1211ad","tid":178644,"uid":378,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-30T05:43:07.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>韓國醉酒佬都幾多下 但你只要唔理佢無做咩特別事 普通行路就好安全 （我覺得安全過日本 日本次次去都見到痴線佬 韓國未試過 只係遇過一個飲醉既人差啲醉左落我到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ）</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n韓國安全過日本<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9a159cc0bc9ed0931fe70436bf693dd4d8a9f0ae","tid":178644,"uid":56963,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-30T05:49:18.000Z","msg":"一個人係韓國真係好難食野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e0ba2dc08c1be97ddfb9f55eb6f3c0c9041eeece","tid":178644,"uid":70643,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-30T05:50:48.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>岩岩比完機票住宿錢就同男朋友分左手<br />\n諗住自己一個去韓國<br />\n但係人生路不熟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有冇人試過有獨遊既經驗</blockquote><br />\n不過一個人去韓國有個唔好處 好多鋪都係for兩個人或以上食 一個好難叫野食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我都煩緊呢樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n想去韓國大部分都係因為d野食</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n去首爾旅遊區識普通話就得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"042b8b6f09916f9022d8f0eb54a6f117039c9d61","tid":178644,"uid":68901,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-30T06:10:58.000Z","msg":"一定掂 好多韓國人識少少英文同普通話 我自己覺得出夜街都無問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7b106991b07b0767c86968b8bfe45f5502fbfc39","tid":178644,"uid":2861,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-30T06:14:57.000Z","msg":"小心醉酒佬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ba4a5d6611b5cbb20fde132de8b6d407b28c21b8","tid":178644,"uid":60151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-30T06:43:23.000Z","msg":"寵寵寵寵寵"},{"pid":"cf24752a058a48de6bafec2b73c327fb2f162094","tid":178644,"uid":29717,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-30T06:47:53.000Z","msg":"夜晚<br />\n唔好去清涼里(如果係巴打夜晚可去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n唔好去弘大，好多醉酒男<br />\n唔好太夜坐地鐵，好多醉酒大叔周街屌人<br />\n<br />\n一般遊客區，大陸店員多過韓國人"},{"pid":"ac5bec5765c9ba92145baeda6182711956ec9601","tid":178644,"uid":18483,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-30T07:05:28.000Z","msg":"其實都安全 不過自己一個女仔去都要小心d<br />\n唔好太夜番酒店 過左11點條街就好少人 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n當然要睇下邊區啦 試過有次住間民宿唔係遊客區<br />\n11點幾返去成條街冇燈 仲勁多麻甩佬 <br />\n真係好淆底<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n好彩個陣有個friend一齊 <br />\n<br />\n另外好多韓國人唔係好識英文 問路最好問後生仔  裝定Google Translate<br />\n交通方面地鐵都去到好多地方 好方便<br />\n<br />\n絲打幾時去？我五月尾都會自己一個去首爾<br />\n如果時間夾到可以一齊食個飯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b435f3171b174fc6c8018bb6df007d5eca29113d","tid":178644,"uid":15256,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-30T07:20:02.000Z","msg":"韓巢地圖好準好方便 <br />\n之前去d韓國人知我係學生 對我好nice<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"199d1174d52817f21e90ba399f775efd068762ab","tid":178644,"uid":83973,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-30T08:22:12.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>其實都安全 不過自己一個女仔去都要小心d<br />\n唔好太夜番酒店 過左11點條街就好少人 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n當然要睇下邊區啦 試過有次住間民宿唔係遊客區<br />\n11點幾返去成條街冇燈 仲勁多麻甩佬 <br />\n真係好淆底<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n好彩個陣有個friend一齊 <br />\n<br />\n另外好多韓國人唔係好識英文 問路最好問後生仔  裝定Google Translate<br />\n交通方面地鐵都去到好多地方 好方便<br />\n<br />\n絲打幾時去？我五月尾都會自己一個去首爾<br />\n如果時間夾到可以一齊食個飯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我六月頭去，夾唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我都想有人同我食飯"},{"pid":"509efbcc60c9f882cd1d7d2e13fe9f4ed1bbdf5f","tid":178644,"uid":83973,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-30T08:24:43.000Z","msg":"仲要機票係預左7日行程<br />\n而家得我一條友都唔知可以點hea7日<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e6f016a9384dab40aa584d31dbcb5d2e6d86a51b","tid":178644,"uid":88336,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-30T08:47:36.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>仲要機票係預左7日行程<br />\n而家得我一條友都唔知可以點hea7日<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n如果唔駛話一定要去好多景點，過充實既旅行，<br />\n你只要日日瞓到自然醒、瞓醒先諗去邊、搭車時間加間唔中蕩失路，時間就會好快過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n不過真心建議夜晚唔好太夜返酒店，9點幾10點返到去就差唔多，反正夜晚除左club果啲都無咩好行；自己一個女仔唔好去club玩，啲韓仔都幾狼<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n利申：剛去完韓國9日，輕鬆慢活，不過都有少量行程"},{"pid":"35fdbaffa35605bd0b65a88dce2a4da695eea6e9","tid":178644,"uid":75495,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-30T12:51:24.000Z","msg":"其實去首爾住宿大家會住邊頭?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2975a7ef560d141dc1fc4a9bca634ebf48ab1181","tid":178644,"uid":74214,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-30T12:56:55.000Z","msg":"一齊去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"02a4c8acc8c6bbd7f3d836ea7cad9d7c2263a591","tid":178644,"uid":6807,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-30T18:06:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>其實都安全 不過自己一個女仔去都要小心d<br />\n唔好太夜番酒店 過左11點條街就好少人 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n當然要睇下邊區啦 試過有次住間民宿唔係遊客區<br />\n11點幾返去成條街冇燈 仲勁多麻甩佬 <br />\n真係好淆底<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n好彩個陣有個friend一齊 <br />\n<br />\n另外好多韓國人唔係好識英文 問路最好問後生仔  裝定Google Translate<br />\n交通方面地鐵都去到好多地方 好方便<br />\n<br />\n絲打幾時去？我五月尾都會自己一個去首爾<br />\n如果時間夾到可以一齊食個飯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n韓國人啲英文真係屎到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"79921f380505a234ff9325cd832ba27b98ccda13","tid":178644,"uid":44722,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-30T18:07:21.000Z","msg":"首爾識中文就得"},{"pid":"1b4b049b550569bfb7c053aefbe943a234edb60c","tid":178644,"uid":101078,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-30T18:11:23.000Z","msg":"韓國地鐵有中文 基本上餐廳都有中文餐牌 同埋做旅遊區果啲韓國人都一定識中文 所以一個人去唔識韓文都絕對冇問題 所有嘢都好簡單好易handle 我去過韓國7次 其中一次一個人去左一個月留學 如果有問題想問我好留意解答<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"784b0e145d33a079fdab9abc6c2ba5fa25187631","tid":178644,"uid":101078,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-30T18:14:07.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>韓國地鐵有中文 基本上餐廳都有中文餐牌 同埋做旅遊區果啲韓國人都一定識中文 所以一個人去唔識韓文都絕對冇問題 所有嘢都好簡單好易handle 我去過韓國7次 其中一次一個人去左一個月留學 如果有問題想問我好留意解答<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n樂意 sor9 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ba0625ad5611ac1dbf579538ce92341d158876a4","tid":178644,"uid":14131,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-30T18:17:00.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://www.weekendhk.com/korea/首爾-地鐵-職員騙錢-保障自己方法/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.weekendhk.com%2Fkorea%2F%E9%A6%96%E7%88%BE-%E5%9C%B0%E9%90%B5-%E8%81%B7%E5%93%A1%E9%A8%99%E9%8C%A2-%E4%BF%9D%E9%9A%9C%E8%87%AA%E5%B7%B1%E6%96%B9%E6%B3%95%2F&d=oGSqBYpvdEZZERTBUGrA0p7TfgnX9jywtYe9GXZmhCU%3D&h=410e54a1\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.weekendhk.com/korea/首爾-地鐵-職員騙錢-保障自己方法/</a>"},{"pid":"853f6bc0314646eb462f7b980af93a6d932a215a","tid":178644,"uid":27083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-30T19:26:28.000Z","msg":"去完覺得一個人去韓國慢活好爽<br />\n不過一個人去係好少野食到，度度都2人份量<br />\n同埋啲韓國人好好人，見你一個女仔拎住個喼會幫手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n利申去完韓國翻嚟瘦左2kg<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2c3c289b849ab4d0f08e8e2b687ddd0524404496","tid":178644,"uid":54812,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-01T11:50:31.000Z","msg":"有無人6月尾去"},{"pid":"3d44fa2ae95f5b9fb1b21009ca4e7a8d70976390","tid":178644,"uid":54812,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-01T11:51:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有無人6月尾去</blockquote><br />\n驚1丁友去到無啖好食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cd4894edcd8f873f4d8598e879389647965d4eeb","tid":178644,"uid":38338,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-01T16:06:30.000Z","msg":"我下年一月自己去首爾<img src=\"/